    "text": "Validation6. (1) Notwithstanding the provisions of paragraph (a) ofsubsection (1) and subsection (2), of section 8 of the Powersof Attorney (Amendment) Act, No. 28 of 2022, every powerof attorney executed prior to October 25, 2022 and whichhas not been registered on or prior to the date ofcommencement of this Act shall be deemed to be valid for aperiod of two years from October 25, 2022, and be submittedfor registration to the Registrar General within such periodof two years."
